title: Compact Laser Printer with Wireless and Duplex | Brother™ HL-L2340DW
description: The Brother™ HL-L2340DW is a reliable, affordable monochrome laser printer for home or small office use. This desk-friendly, compact printer with an up to 250-sheet capacity tray connects with ease via wireless networking or Hi-Speed USB 2.0 interface and prints crisp black and white documents at up to 27ppm‡. Print from compatible mobile devices over your wireless network‡. Automatic duplex printing helps save paper. 1-year limited warranty plus free phone support for life of your product.
